Rendered artifacts from this template may include deterministic `AHRE_SLOT_START:<slotId>` / `AHRE_SLOT_END:<slotId>` markers. AhRE reports those slots in recipe output and inventory so agents know where business-specific logic belongs without reading generated files first.
